        <item>
            <title>Red Bull 制极速 FPV 无人机【有片睇】   最高时速 350 km/h 媲美 F1 赛车</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/01/red-bull-fpv/life-tech/sport-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=red-bull-fpv</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/01/red-bull-fpv/life-tech/sport-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 11:47:27 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[航拍]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[运动科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[F1 赛车]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[FPV Drone]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[空拍机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[航拍机]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1222104</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>一般人玩的无人机平均飞行速度约为每小时 60 公里，是次与 Red Bull RB20 竞速的 FPV 速度竟然达每小时 300 公里，最高速度达每小时 350 公里。这款 FPV 由 Red Bull 与 Dutch Drone God 团队合力研发的 FPV 只需 4 秒就可加速至每小时 300 公里。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_33069"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9pEqyr_uT-k?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>Red Bull 日前在 YouTube 上传了一条影片，展示旗下 Red Bull 车队的 Max Verstappen 驾驶 RB20 F1 赛车在英国银石赛场上与 FPV 竞速。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222112" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/worldsfastestcamerad-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/worldsfastestcamerad-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/worldsfastestcamerad.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在直接与 Max Verstappen 对决之前，这架 FPV 与旧款 RB8 赛车直线对决，结果可见 RB8 加速在 FPV 面前简直不值一提，这架 FPV 只需 4 秒就加速到每小时 300 公里以上，加速度比 RB8 快接近两倍。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222114" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/worldsfastestcamerad-2-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/worldsfastestcamerad-2-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/worldsfastestcamerad-2.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>这架 FPV 为了突破极速，其设计造型与一般无人机不同，相较下更像是火箭。Dutch Drone God 与 Red Bull 工程师耗费一年时间，克服机身过热、续航力及空气力学等问题，最终成功创造史上最快 FPV 。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222115" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/worldsfastestcamerad-3-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/worldsfastestcamerad-3-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/worldsfastestcamerad-3.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>这款 FPV 需要由操控者手动控制，机上配备高速 4K 镜头和无线传送系统。据报这款 FPV 的操控者除了要小心赛道上不同障碍，更需要小心留意不可太贴近 F1 赛车，以免被赛车高速行驶时的气流影响航行。</p><figure class="aligncenter no-info-img"><div class="popup-gallery"><p>Max Verstappen 在赛事后表示这个画面「是 F1 最漂亮的画面」，犹如打机时才看见的画面。</p></div></figure><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9pEqyr_uT-k">Red Bull@YouTube</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/11/3-chinese-arrested-in-west-kowloon-because-of-small-unmanned-aircraft-order/life-tech/drone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">3 名中国男女涉违反《小型无人机令》     先后于西九文化区被捕</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/01/red-bull-fpv/life-tech/sport-tech/">Red Bull 制极速 FPV 无人机【有片睇】   最高时速 350 km/h 媲美 F1 赛车</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
