        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Google 修改 Wear OS   进一步改善电池续航力</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/01/wear-os-co-processor-improve-battery-life-galaxy-smartwatch/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=wear-os-co-processor-improve-battery-life-galaxy-smartwatch</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/01/wear-os-co-processor-improve-battery-life-galaxy-smartwatch/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美凤]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 05:00:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[潮流手表]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Wear OS]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221978</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>现时大部分 Wear OS 智能手表的电池续航时间只有一至两天，需要更长续航力的用户，可能需要考虑运动手环或搭载自家操作系统但功能稍逊的智能手表。为了解决这个问题，Google 现正尝试对 Wear OS 作针对性的修改，将处理通知的工作交由智能手表内的协同处理器负责。</p><p><span id="more-1221978"></span></p><p>数年前，Wear OS 引入了 MCU 超低功耗协同处理器的支持，心率追踪和步数计等较小的任务都交由协同处理器处理。现在，Google 进一步容许 MCU 处理从智能手机发送的讯息通知、回复通知和清除通知等任务。这项转变的好处是 MCU 处理健康追踪和所有通知的时候，手表的处理器能够保持休眠状态，让电耗得以降低，从而将电池续航力延长。</p><p>日前发表的 OnePlus Watch 2 是首款采用此新功能的 Wear OS 智能手表，厂方宣称续航力可达 100 小时。以往 Wear OS 有不少为人诟病的缺点，随著 Google 和 Samsung 宣布合作并开发 Wear OS 3 之后，就有了大幅度的改善。Google 亦著手对该系统进行不少改进，吸引了小米、OPPO 和 OnePlus 等品牌加入，不过一直使用 Wear OS 推出智能手表的钟表品牌 Fossil，早前则确认退出智能手表市场。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.sammobile.com/news/wear-os-co-processor-improve-battery-life-galaxy-smartwatch/">sammobile</a></p><p>&nbsp;<br /><b>相关文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/oneplus-watch-2-wear-os/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">OnePlus Watch 2 发表，改用 Wear OS 定价约 2,348 港元</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/29/fossil-wear-os-smartwatch-business-exit/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Fossil 专注传统钟表产品，宣布撤出 Wear OS 智能手表市场</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/28/samsung-google-reportedly-testing-wear-os-5/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Wear OS 5 传今年推出   Galaxy Watch 7 系列或率先预载</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/01/wear-os-co-processor-improve-battery-life-galaxy-smartwatch/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/">Google 修改 Wear OS   进一步改善电池续航力</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
